[26:48] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'remap out to only the bottom left half of the screen and try it again. So, if you are like me and want to go crazy with an AmbuLed setup, just keep this in mind that depending on where you\'re installing the LEDs, you might run into the same dilemma of where to best map'

[27:00] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'them out if you install any of them perpendicular to the screen. So, I\'ve talked a lot about the features, but how does it all come together? Well, once you have it dialed into your liking, the performance is nothing short of amazing. Here, you can really start to get a feel for just how'

[27:13] [scene:talk]
