[27:26] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'program, but I would recommend using the same Muzata diffuser channels that I used for the vertical pillars on the wall to get rid of these hot spots. Next, I have to call out what might be the most impressive part of everything, which is how instantaneous the'

