[28:21] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'Disney Plus, SignalRGB isn\'t able to see what\'s on the screen. So, to fix this, go into your browser, go to settings, system, and turn off graphics accelerator, and just like that, SignalRGB is now able to see the screen. So, switching over to hardware, and the'

